  <brief_title>Comparison of the Evaluation of CAD by CT AngioScan and Coronary Angiogram</brief_title>
  <acronym>CTAS-MCAS</acronym>
  <official_title>Comparison of the Evaluation of CAD by CT AngioScan and Coronary Angiogram in Patient as Part of Preoperative Evaluation in Ascending Aorta Replacement Surgery Patients.</official_title>
